-- ===========================================================================
-- World generation + customization for the MASTER (forest) shard.
-- 世界生成与定制 — 主世界（森林）分片。
--
-- This Lua table is the server's world-generation blueprint. Every creature,
-- resource, and season is configured here. Customize it to shape your surface
-- world. Key fields:
-- 此 Lua 表是服务端的世界生成蓝图。所有生物、资源和季节均在此配置。
-- 通过定制此文件来塑造你的地表世界。关键字段：
--   id / location / name -> world identity ("forest" here; "cave" for caves)
--                           世界标识（此处为 "forest"；洞穴为 "cave"）
--   world_size           -> "default" | "small" | "medium" | "large" | "huge"
--                           世界大小
--   overrides            -> per-setting frequency / 各设置项的频率值
--
-- Most overrides take a frequency word: "default" | "never" | "rare" |
-- "uncommon" | "often" | "mostly" | "always" (some accept their own values).
-- "default" = vanilla behavior. Both shards must keep
-- required_prefabs = { "multiplayer_portal" } so players can travel between
-- the surface and caves.
-- 大多数覆盖项使用频率词。保留 "default" 即使用原版设置。
-- 两个分片均须保留 required_prefabs = { "multiplayer_portal" } 以确保互通。
--
-- Easiest way to produce: configure the world on the in-game "Host Game" screen,
-- host once, then copy the generated file from the save.
-- 推荐生成方式：在游戏内 "Host Game" 界面配置世界，开服一次后从存档中复制生成的文件。
-- ===========================================================================
